 曼彻斯特，希顿公园（已售完）</b><br /> <b>20 - 曼彻斯特，希顿公园（已售完）</b><br /> <b>25 – 伦敦，温布利球场（已售完）</b><br /> <b>26 – 伦敦，温布利球场（已售完）</b><br /> <b>30 – 伦敦，温布利球场（已售完）</b></p><p> <b>2025 年 8 月</b><br /><b>2 – 伦敦，温布利球场（已售完）</b><br /> <b>3 – 伦敦，温布利球场（已售完）</b><br /> <b>8 – 爱丁堡，苏格兰煤气默里菲尔德体育场（已售完）</b><br /> <b>9 – 爱丁堡，苏格兰煤气默里菲尔德体育场（已售完）</b><br /> <b>12 – 爱丁堡，苏格兰煤气默里菲尔德体育场（已售完）</b><br /> <b>16 – 都柏林，克罗克公园（已售完）</b><br /> <b>17 – 都柏林，克罗克公园（已售完）</b></p><p> <b>2025 年 9 月</b><br /><b>27 - 伦敦，温布利球场</b><br /><b>28 - 伦敦，温布利球场</b></p><p>最初的门票售完后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-warn-fans-that-people-attempting-to-sell-tickets-on-the-secondary-market-will-have-them-cancelled-by-the-promoters-3789345">绿洲警告粉丝，“试图在二级市场上出售门票的人”将“被主办方取消”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-ticket-sales-culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-calls-for-review-into-dynamic-pricing-and-secondary-ticket-sites-3789694">文化大臣丽莎·南迪呼吁对有争议的动态定价做法进行审查</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keir-starmer-responds-to-oasis-price-hikes-calling-them-depressing-3790633">总理基尔·斯塔默称价格上涨“令人沮丧”</a> ，而竞争和市场管理局、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ministers-looking-to-ban-dynamic-pricing-in-ireland-after-oasis-reunion-surge-ticket-controversy-3791228">爱尔兰政府</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-european-commission-reportedly-investigating-dynamic-pricing-amid-oasis-tickets-controversy-3790240">欧洲委员会</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-cma-launches-official-government-enquiry-into-dynamic-surge-ticket-pricing-3790957">现在将对此问题进行调查。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-european-commission-reportedly-investigating-dynamic-pricing-amid-oasis-tickets-controversy-3790240">委员会</a>。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="508" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;4697778